Package: appifyr
Type: Package
Title: appifyr: Write R Get Apps!
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: person("Reto", "Wyss", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "reto.wyss.ch@gmail.com")
Description: appifyr enables you to build apps from function definitions.
    Output from appify can be rendered in an Rmd file or may be saved to
    a file as html. To run apps created with appifyr you'll need OpenCPU.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
